1. in google chrome go to manage extentions
2. enable developer mode
3. click load unpacked
4. select folder 'chrome extention' folder




what does this extention do?

it connects to the secure websocket chat's backend
when there is a new message it will display the message as a popup and the extention icon will display number of unread messages


what can i do with it?

you can clear the unread message icon by left clicking the extention icon and clicking 'Clear Badge'
you can uncheack 'Enable Notifications'. when disabled it will no longer give you a popup for new messages